      <section name='chat'>

         <para number='1' comment='Hello'>
         Hey, you know that chick who used to dance alot, everynight she'd be there shaking what she'd, amn when I tell you she was cool she was red hot, I mean she was steaming. Oh, hello, its been so long since anyone has been here, how did you get here, are you ok? They told me someone would come one day, but I really did'nt expect it to be this long!!
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='who/dino'>
         Ah, I am a bot they left here many many years ago when they abandoned Wisp, you know it used to be the principal planet in the Cloud system. The curator told me that if he did not return word to me that he may have come to an untimely end, but he hoped someone would eventually come, I guess you must be that person, I was left behind to offer any assistance that you might need, so how can I be of help to you?
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='where/bar'>
         Ah, this is my joint, you know anybody who was anybody used to be in here when the planet was alive and kicking. You know this time over at Johhny's place, well this chick got up and she slapped Johnny's face, man we just fell about the place, but if that chick don't wanna know then forget her. Errr, sorry, I digress, it has been such a long time. This is where the people of Wisp would come to socialise, eat, drink and be merry.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='wisp'>
         Aaah yes Wisp, in its heyday, this was the principal planet in the Cloud system. But due to overpopulation and irresponsible industry practices, pollution built up to the extent that it was a very hazardous place to be. So they all went to the other planets, there was talk of building an orbital station around Cumulus too. They left me here to assist anyone returning to reopen the planet.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='cumulus'>
         Cumulus was always the second planet of the system, but they left here many years ago and it is now the epicentre of the Cloud system, they even took the palace, my, what an engineering feat that was I can tell you.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='cloudbase'>
         Cloudbase is a character from Cloudarian legend, one day he shall come forth and free Wisp so that it can be recolonised and take its rightful place as the principal world in the Cloud system. There was talk of building an orbital station around Cumulus, many talked of naming it after this fictional character, but I dont know if that ever really happened.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='nimbus'>
         Yes Nimbus was never really a very nice place, its the Biological planet in the Cloud system, not many people live there as it is pretty unhospitable, but it remains an important sphere in the system.
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='cloud'>
         Well what can I say about the Cloud system that isnt already known, its one of the oldest systems in the universe, steeped in tradition and also one of the most technologically advanced. It used to be amongst the wealthiest too, but its been many years since I have either left this planet or had contact with anyone, so I don't really know anymore, though I am sure the Cloudarians have done all to maintain that status.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='cloudarian'>
         The Cloudarians are a mighty race, amonst the forefathers of the universe, peaceful, friendly and great traders too. They are also known for being the most attractive also!!
         </para>

         <para number='10' comment='museum'>
         The museum used to hold many thousands of artifacts dating back to the dawn of time, most of them were priceless. But they all got moved when Wisp was evacuated. My best friend is the curator, but I fear as I have heard no word from him, that his worst fears were realised. I hope you can find out what happened to him for me.
         </para>

         <para number='11' comment='curator'>
         The curator was a close and personal friend of mine, he told me that should anything happen to him, that he would leave some important information somewhere, but he really was'nt making very much sense at all, he seemed to be under an awful lot of pressure the last few days before the evacuation,  you should check out his office and sleeping quarters, thats where I think he might have left it
         </para>

         <para number='12' comment='reactor'>
         Well, I don't know much about reactors, but I do know the one we have here on Wisp is very old, just before the evacuation they were talking about replacing it as they could not run it at 100% due to its age.
         </para>

         <para number='13' comment='challenge/puzzle/task/mission'>
         My friend the curator was'nt making very much sense on his last few days here on Wisp. He told me something had been stolen and that he had a strong lead. He also said he was worried they might get him, so he left some important information in his diary, thats all I know, sorry I can't help you any more than that.
         </para>

         <para number='14' comment='red door pass'>
         Yes, the Red Door Pass, suprisingly enough that is used to open the Red Door!!    The colours may have faded over the passage of time, I do know that this pass opens the door to the curators office. To use it swipe the door pass in the card reader outside his office.
         </para>

         <para number='15' comment='blue door pass'>
         Oh goodness me!!  Such a long time, and there were so many different door pass colours, they were used mainly in the accommodation area, but some were used in this complex, but I am sorry, I really dont know what that one is for.
         </para>

         <para number='16' comment='green door pass'>
         I don't know what they're doing but they laugh alot behind the green door!!    Hmmm, sorry, not sure which door that one opens, you will just have to try it and see.
         </para>

         <para number='17' comment='yellow door pass'>
         The Yellow Door Pass.    Nope, you got me, not a clue!!
         </para>

         <para number='18' comment='door pass'>
         Yes, the planet used to have door passes to gain access to various areas, they were mainly used in the accommodation block, but important areas had them too.
         </para>

         <para number='19' comment='food'>
         Yes, we serve food, of course we do!!! This is my bar and grill, though our range is pretty limited these days, no supplies you see, and to be honest!! the stock is a little old!!! So you pays your money you takes your chance.
         </para>

         <para number='20' comment='drink'>
         Oh yes, we have that aplenty here, most popular joing on the planet, well it was when there were people on it. The ale matures nicely over the years so why don't you try one, I cleaned the pipes out this morning and we can supply all you need!
         </para>

         <para number='21' comment='nomatch'>
         Now, I am sure that where you come from that makes perfect sense, but you might have to run it by me again in a different way if you want me to understand and reply.
         </para>

