         <para number='1' comment='Molly slaps - loc 401 -'>
         Molly quickly steps back, draws her hand back and slaps you hard across the face, you pay to touch or keep your hands to yourself she says, but I warn you I am not cheap! You dont't look the sort that can afford my services anyway, so perhaps you might want to buy some information instead, I have some very rich high ranking clients who can be a little indiscrete with their pillow talk.
